STATE
v.
Jonathan Anthony UZZELL. No. 169P08. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 11, 2008. Sandra Wallace-Smith, Assistant Attorney General, C. Branson Vickory, III, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 8th day of April 2008 by Defendant to Appoint Counsel:

"Motion Dismissed as moot by order of the Court in conference this the 11th day of June 2008."
